snippet.title: Blockland Physics Preview
snippet.description:
The game is Blockland: http://blockland.us
The song is Annie - Chewing Gum


This is a preview of physics in Blockland, which is slated for release with version 11 (UPDATE: v11 has been released, the physics are in the game).  As usual this will be a free update, so feel free to buy the game whenever.

Blockland is a multiplayer sandbox game where you build with bricks that are similar to (but legally distinct from) legos.  It is an indy game made using the torque engine.  Check it out at http://www.Blockland.us
